project_descr: Assist in food security improvement in the Gaza Strip

outputs.output_descr: The project's aim at supporting the resilience of the Gaza Strip residents through supporting the affected beekeepers, and restoring their livelihoods activities which was completely lost as a result of the ongoing crises and frequent Israeli incursions against Gaza. The project will target 364 of small beekeepers in Gaza Strip, to enable them to resume their productive activities and to restore their sustainable income.

project_title: improve food security in marginalized area in gaza strip
